376
00:23:32.867 --> 00:23:33.967
What?

377
00:23:33.967 --> 00:23:36.767
Come on! Let's head off right away!

378
00:23:36.767 --> 00:23:39.167
What? Hey! Don't pull me!

379
00:23:39.167 --> 00:23:42.767
I'm fed up with occult already.

380
00:23:42.767 --> 00:23:44.767
You can say that again.

